overview: When Chadder ventures into the Hokeybadjokey Swamp, he's just hoping to find an interesting story for his school newspaper. But when Chadder's swamp guide, Fraider, offers to take him to the Monster Croc...the adventure is just beginning!
tagline: Join Chadder Chipmunk in fearlessly shining god's light!
title: Chadder's Bayou Adventure
